      "response_body": "\r\n<html>\r\n<!-- include new style master - SC 24 08 15 -->\r\n <link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"https://ww3.wirral.gov.uk/css/newmaster.css\" />\r\n <head></head>\r\n \r\n<style type=\"text/css\">\r\n\r\na\r\n{\r\n\tcolor:#000;\r\n\tline-height: 250%; \r\n}\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n<script>\r\nfunction nextDiv(a)\r\n{\r\n\tvar nextID=document.getElementById(\"div\"+a);\r\n\tvar thisID=document.getElementById(\"div\"+(a-1));\r\n\tthisID.style.visibility=\"hidden\";\r\n\tthisID.style.display=\"none\";\r\n\tnextID.style.visibility=\"visible\";\r\n\tnextID.style.display=\"inline\";\r\n\t//alert(a);\r\n}\r\nfunction prevDiv(a)\r\n{\r\n\tvar prevID=document.getElementById(\"div\"+a);\r\n\tvar thisID=document.getElementById(\"div\"+(a+1));\r\n\tthisID.style.visibility=\"hidden\";\r\n\tthisID.style.display=\"none\";\r\n\tprevID.style.visibility=\"visible\";\r\n\tprevID.style.display=\"inline\";\r\n\t//alert(a);\r\n}\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<body>       \r\n       \r\n<!--\r\n<p>Your green wheelie bin is for any rubbish that you don&rsquo;t recycle. Please think about what you are throwing away. If you are new to the area please call us for a bin. on 0151 606 2004</p>\r\n<p>Please place your bin out before 7am on your collection day below and remove as soon as possible on the same day after emptying. also number your bin with your house number to avoid other people using it irresponsibly.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Have you really thought about what you&rsquo;re throwing away?</p>\r\n<p>All the waste in your bin will end up in landfill; a big hole in the ground which is filled with our rubbish and then covered over, which creates gases that can effect climate change. Plus we are running out of space in our landfill sites and Government are imposing strict penalties when we go over our limit. This could impact on your Council Tax.</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"/LGCL/100006/200084/851/content_0002161.html\">Did you know that two thirds of your bin content could be recycled?</a></p>\r\n--><div id='div1'  style='width:100%;'><!-- w-ONE-d-Friday -->\r\n\r\n\t<label style=\"color: white; background-color:#393; font-weight: Bold; width:90%;\">\r\n    \t&nbsp;The Dates Below Are For<br/>&nbsp;Non recyclable (green bin)\r\n    \t<br/>&nbsp;The next collection is:<br />\r\n\t</label>\r\n\r\n\t<fieldset style=\"padding-left:3px; border:none;\">\r\n<legend>Information unavailable</legend><br><span style='font-weight:bold;'>The next collection date for this road is currently not available,  Please try again later</span>\r\n\t\t<ul>\r\n<!--<table class=\"collectionDates\" cellspacing=\"0\">-->\r\n\r\n</ul>\r\n<!--</table>-->\r\n <!-- <p><a href=\"/my-services/environment-and-planning/recycling-rubbish-and-waste/bins/green-refuse-bins\" target=\"_parent\">What can I put in my green bin</a></p>-->\r\n <!-- calendar button woz ere -->\r\n\t\t\t<span><a class=\"wg-button\" style=\"text-align:center; \" href=\"https://ww3.wirral.gov.uk/recycling/pdf/2025/GreenGrey_10_FriWk2.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" onClick=\"ga('send', 'event', 'Recycling', 'Download', 'PDF Non recycleable (green bin)');ga('send', 'pageview', this.href);\">\r\n\t\t\t<!--<img src=\"DownloadCalendar2.jpg\" alt=\"Printable Calendar\" border=\"0\"/>-->\r\n Download a printable bin calendar\r\n </a></span>\r\n\r\n</fieldset>\r\n\r\n<!--<br />-->\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Google Analytics -->\r\n<script>\r\n  (function(i,s,o,g,r,a,m){i['GoogleAnalyticsObject']=r;i[r]=i[r]||function(){\r\n  (i[r].q=i[r].q||[]).push(arguments)},i[r].l=1*new Date();a=s.createElement(o),\r\n  m=s.getElementsByTagName(o)[0];a.async=1;a.src=g;m.parentNode.insertBefore(a,m)\r\n  })(window,document,'script','//www.google-analytics.com/analytics.js','ga');\r\n\r\n  ga('create', 'UA-3100709-1', 'auto');\r\n  ga('send', 'pageview');\r\n\r\n</script>\r\n<!-- end Google Analytics -->\r\n</body>\r\n</html>",
